## Why This Is Asked

This question probes practical mastery of PrivateLink in multi-region setups, tenant isolation, and PCI logging. It tests how to combine API gateway throttling with ENI policies, and how to design observability and DR.

## Key Concepts

- PrivateLink endpoint policies and isolation
- Per-tenant throttling with API keys/usage plans
- PCI log governance with VPC Flow Logs, CloudWatch, KMS
- Cross-region DR testing with failover

## Code Example

